Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Demon Ninja Hoshiyomi captured\NKagome and used her spiritual powers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:21.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to restore the frightening power\nof the Naginata of Kenkon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! What're we gonna do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're being sucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're gonna save Kagome\nfrom the hands of that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no matter what we have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Tetsusaiga still {\i1}isn't....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything is possible if\nyou put your spirit into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:53.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything in the universe\ndisappears eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sadness and happiness,\nall fade with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even this world will\nsomeday be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should give up\nyour senseless struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and die quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You do not understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Against the Naginata of Kenkon,\nyou cannot win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Naginata of Kenkon\nis invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want this girl back\nso badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You love this girl that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I love Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will gladly trade my life for hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please return Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said that nothing\nlasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even with the passing\nof {\i1}time....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even{\i0} with the passing\nof {\i1}time....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something called\nlove which never dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akitoki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so impulsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At times like these,\nhe should just keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as you said, it is true that\NI am but a weak human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, because we are so weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,humans can understand the\npain of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and can show kindness\nand compassion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I believe that such\nfeelings last forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph! Feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If humans had kindness,\nif they understood pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,why did Tsukiyomi\nseal me away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What humans did to me,\NI will repay with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So die knowing how I feel-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are finally able\nto meet once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi, what do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted you to remember\nonce {\i1}again....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the feelings you once felt\ntowards humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The kindness you showed {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The days we once shared together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, Tsukiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save your worries for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not want to hold you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can\nrun away from us, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:40.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not even worth fearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You go through such\n{\i1}pains....for{\i0} a lone woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Letting a lowly {\i1}human....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Letting {\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,steal your {\i1}heart....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I even changed my\nname to Hoshiyomi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how much\NI cared about Tsukiyomi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abiraunken Sowaka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've used too much\nof your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we continue hunting down\ndemons like {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,your life will {\i1}be....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late to give up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons who begrudge us\nwill keep coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! There must be a place where\nwe need not fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere we can live\nin peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here are the corpses of\nthe demons you spoke {\i1}of....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are 222 of them in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gathered them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you have everything\nto complete
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the ultimate weapon which\npossesses the power of yin and yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That time, in order to find a place for\nyou and me where there would be no fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:22.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I asked Kaijinbo to forge this\NNaginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I needed a weapon that equaled\nthe power you possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that you would not need to\nexpend any more of your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:35.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did it all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you betray me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This naginata is truly amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Behold, Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as I have this Naginata of Kenkon,\nyou need not use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this, we need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if a hundred, a thousand\ndemons attack us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Naginata of Kenkon\nis very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must seal it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to live in peace,\nwithout having to {\i1}fight....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must have absolute power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi is becoming possessed\nby the Naginata of Kenkon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If nothing is done...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin! Pyo! To! Sha! Kai! Chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Retsu! Zai!\N- Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such frightening demonic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil {\i1}powers....{\i0} Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The calamity has been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will release you from\nthe seal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}strength....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:11.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ho-shi....yomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:42.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were just a human, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:52.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was no way you could love\nme, a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you telling me the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not saying that I\ndid not betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I wanted to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the spell of the\NNaginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to release you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it all because of\nmy own weakness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it because my heart\ndid not have faith in Tsukiyomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that this darkness was born?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My body may no longer exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but my feelings are\nyours eternally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's way too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all much too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Naginata of Kenkon has\nreturned to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it thirsts for blood even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's all right.\NThe blade didn't touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Let me down.\NI'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I now possess absolute power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no regrets whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall rid the world of humans\nwith the Naginata of Kenkon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still going on about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi died for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you ignore her sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}Tetsusaiga....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi was human,\nbut she was not weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She possessed a much\nstronger heart than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who\nbetrayed yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You became bewitched by the\NNaginata of Kenkon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because your own heart\nwas weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence, wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:57.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lay a hand on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,protect Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lay a hand on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die, Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You impudent half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:42.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:49.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}power....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My power hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your spiritual powers have all\nbeen absorbed by the Naginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:15:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there something we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} If we take the naginata\naway from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,something may be {\i1}possible....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be killed before\nwe can steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, whom I care for deeply,\nis fighting, while {\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:33.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:16:59.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I love you, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-Akitoki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are weak, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to rush to death,\nso be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lend me your strength, {\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! My power has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be grateful to Akitoki.\NIt's all because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! Thank you, Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then,\nlet's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! What can you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything is powerless against\nthe Naginata of Kenkon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:29.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this! Backlash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's better this {\i1}way....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's better like this,\nright, Tsukiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was a fine joint effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:34.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were in perfect sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He {\i1}is....me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, Hoshiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was a time when I was\npossessed by demonic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I couldn't control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! It's exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, you had Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome embraced you with kindness\nand saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first time was\nwith "sit."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looking back, he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not kind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- You should be! You little pipsqueak!\N- What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, {\i1}now....{\i0} There are\ndifferent forms of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- please take care of yourself.\N- Shut up! You fake, lecherous monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't call me a fake. I won't argue\nabout being a lecher, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had deep feelings for Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if they would never be reciprocated,\nmy feelings will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're speaking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!\NWhat is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:40.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suzaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:44.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you should change\nsuch a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It does not suit someone\nas beautiful as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Change it to Kagome.\NIt's a lovely name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How about we continue the\njourney together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you were going that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}no....{\i0} Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Akitoki Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And let me tell you that I\nhave had many adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why just the other {\i1}day....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Higurashi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hojo?\NYou're daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep sighing and\nhappiness will run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind this silly family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:24.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be quiet. It'll be over quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the ones killing\nmonks and shrine-keepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard the demon was a\nfemale with an infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this {\i1}infant....{\i0} Could it be\nmore frightening than the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:53.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A priest like you should be able\nto see the border
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between this life and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Entei, The Demon Horse Unleashed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's just a stupid horse!
